二.加密Linux分区

1.cryptsetup luksFormat /dev/vdb1,输入大写YES，然后输入密码

2.解密加密分区cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/vdb1 program

3.对加密分区格式化mkfs.ext4 /dev/mapper/program

4.挂载加密分区mkdir /program ,mount /dev/mapper/program /program

5.永久挂载分区

修改fstab

/dev/mapper/program / ** *** **

6.如果不想输入密码

